l Hall\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1635}, {\"ngram\": \"Fame quarterback\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1655}, {\"ngram\": \"two-time Super Bowl championPeyton Manningwill\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We look forward to providing our Opening Ceremony coverage to audiences at IMAX locations across the country, sharing in this historic moment as the world regathers to witness the spectacular beginning of 16 days of athletic greatness against the backdrop of one of the most beautiful cities in the world,\\\" said Gary Zenkel, President, NBC Olympics.\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 2195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1879, \"end\": 1895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9999999970909812, \"rank\": 2.845343958459427e-09, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}, {\"begin\": 2182, \"end\": 2194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"audiences\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"IMAX locations\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1935}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1954}, {\"ngram\": \"this historic moment\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1987}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"the spectacular beginning\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"16 days\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2058}, {\"ngram\": \"athletic greatness\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2080}, {\"ngram\": \"the backdrop\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2101}, {\"ngram\": \"the most beautiful cities\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2137}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from